column5: Im planning on going Friday night for walleyes from shore,which will be a better choice???   thanks in advance and good luck everyone.
Gores landing. Rice lake is a much better choice then chemong. The walleye are very few in chemong.
I wouldn't waste my time with Chemong either. I haven't heard of anything positive from Chemong over the last couple of years.
If your talking this Friday, you may wanna check the regs. I think the Bridgenorth Causeway is still a sanctuary till the following Friday....
~~~Off Gore Landing on Sat. for Crappies, 2 sneakie eye decided to take my bait instead, told them to stay in the same spot and I'll be back next weekend
Im thinkin the same thing as well Ron, it red flagged me as well, check the regs on that one before you show up, on the bright side youll likely have the spot to yourself
